          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Measurements of the average number of neutrons emitted",
                "in the fission of some uranium and plutonium isotopes."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "This article contains three parts:",
                "Part I. Page 123.",
                "Relative measurements of the average number of",
                "neutrons emitted in the thermal fission of U233, U235,",
                "Pu239, and Pu241.",
                "V.I.Kalashnikova,V.I.Lebedev,L.A.Mikaelyan,",
                "P.E.Spivak,V.P.Zakharova",
                "Part II. Page 127.",
                "Dependence of the number of neutrons emitted",
                "in the fission of heavy nuclei on the excitation",
                "energy of the fissionable nucleus.",
                "V.I.Kalashnikova, A.V.Krasnushkin, V.I.Lebedev,",
                "M.I.Pevzner, V.P.Zakharova",
                "Part III. Page 131.",
                "Absolute evaluation of the average number of",
                "neutrons emitted in the fission of some isotopes of",
                "uranium and plutonium.",
                "V.I.Kalashnikova,V.I.Lebedev,P.E.Spivak,V.P.Zakharova.",
                "In \"V.I.Kalashnikov\" (in part III) there is a misprint,",
                " right \"V.I.Kalashnikova\", see Parts I, II on pages",
                " 123, 127 of AEC-TR-2435,vol.1.",
                ".Of compiler M.M.",
                " This article was presented at 55MOSCOW ( candidates to",
                "55GENEVA were discussed),",
                "and as mentioned in R,UCRL-50400,v.2,rev.2,1976,",
                "at 55GENEVA it was reported by M.S.Kozodaev at",
                "discussion of P/592 - see 55GENEVA,vol.2,",
                "p.228(English), p.258(Russian edition).",
                "In \"V.I.Kalashnikov\" there is probably a misprint,",
                " right \"V.I.Kalashnikova\", see Parts I, II on pages",
                " 123, 127 of AEC-TR-2435,vol.1."
              ]
            }
          ],
